const bodyBase = 'text-base dark:bg-dark-bg dark:text-cloud-gray'

export const basic = {
  html: '',
  body: `bg-cloud-gray ${bodyBase}`,
  lightBorder: 'border-cloud-gray',
  lightBg: 'bg-cloud-gray',
  aside: 'bg-deep-space',
  asideBrand: 'bg-dark-bg text-white',
  asideMenuCloseLg: 'text-white',
  asideMenuLabel: 'text-cloud-gray',
  asideMenuItem: 'hover:bg-electric-teal/20',
  asideMenuItemActive: 'font-bold text-electric-teal',
  asideMenuItemInactive: 'text-cloud-gray',
  asideSubmenuList: 'bg-dark-surface bg-opacity-50',
  navBarItemLabel: 'text-deep-space',
  navBarItemLabelHover: 'hover:text-electric-teal',
  navBarItemLabelActiveColor: 'text-electric-teal',
  navBarMenuListUpperLabel: 'bg-cloud-gray',
  tableTr: 'lg:hover:bg-cloud-gray/50',
  tableTrOdd: 'lg:bg-cloud-gray/20',
  overlay: 'from-deep-space via-dark-bg to-deep-space'
}

export const white = {
  html: 'scrollbars-light',
  body: `bg-white ${bodyBase}`,
  lightBorder: 'border-cloud-gray',
  lightBg: 'bg-cloud-gray',
  aside: 'bg-white border-r border-cloud-gray',
  asideBrand: '',
  asideMenuCloseLg: '',
  asideMenuLabel: 'dark:text-cloud-gray',
  asideMenuItem: 'text-electric-teal hover:text-deep-space dark:text-white',
  asideMenuItemActive: 'font-bold text-deep-space dark:text-white',
  asideMenuItemInactive: '',
  asideSubmenuList: 'bg-cloud-gray',
  navBarItemLabel: 'text-electric-teal',
  navBarItemLabelHover: 'hover:text-deep-space',
  navBarItemLabelActiveColor: 'text-deep-space',
  navBarMenuListUpperLabel: 'bg-cloud-gray',
  tableTr: 'lg:hover:bg-cloud-gray',
  tableTrOdd: 'lg:bg-cloud-gray/50',
  overlay: 'from-white via-cloud-gray to-white'
}
